OL,3,CFormer Wales Reform leader charged
OL,4,Cwith bribery offences by Met Police
OL,6,FThe investigation has been led by
OL,7,Fdetectives from the Met Office's
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Command. They say a
OL,9,Fman was previously interviewed under
OL,10,Fcaution on 3 March, 2022 in connection
OL,11,Fwith bribery allegations.
OL,13,FFurther enquiries were carried out by
OL,14,Fofficers and after authorisation by
OL,15,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service Counter
OL,16,FTerrorism Division, Gill was
OL,17,Fsubsequently charged.
